{"tid":2163100,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)再造戰士1-4","createTime":"2020-08-18T12:51:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T19:13:35.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"39a55218ef6134fdf809b0c7247b609119277e23","tid":2163100,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:51:35.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5hnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=bbfd9058\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5hnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=2dc2ddc1\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5hnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=40f9c65c\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/93/Universal_soldier_ver1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F93%2FUniversal_soldier_ver1.jpg&h=dde010a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.越戰後，美國政府進行了一項絕密的科學計劃。科學家們將越戰中犧牲的士兵的屍體冰凍起來，植入電腦晶片，輸入戰爭程序，將他們改造成為新一代的戰爭機器人――「再造戰士」，這些機器人沒有情感和以前的記憶，只有冰冷的殺戮武器。士兵盧克（尚格&middot;雲頓 Jean-Claude Van Damme 飾）和班長安德魯（杜夫&middot;朗格 Dolph Lundgren 飾）就是其中兩員，他們被派往參加一場新的戰爭。戰爭中，兩人的晶片突然出錯.....<br />\n<br />\n2.尚克勞德範達美重返&ldquo;魔鬼命令&rdquo;戰場，再度披掛上場演出的生平第一部續集，當年人類異想天開的創造出宇宙戰士，到最後卻集體叛變。毫無人性、感情的宇宙士中，魯克（尚克勞範達美飾演）是一個改造失敗的例子，因為他殘存的人性，使得他在第一集裡，拯救了人類。<br />\n這次，魯克憑著他的經驗，成為改造宇宙戰士計劃的最佳指導。在魯克的監督之下，第二代的宇宙戰士設備更新穎、功能更強大。一旦他們失去控制，情況將無法收拾。不料，瑕疵再度出現，新一代的宇宙戰士，再度失控，危害人類的存亡。於是魯克再度出擊，務必確保人類的生存...<br />\n<br />\n3.20世紀60年代，美國的勢力向亞洲滲透，為此政府實行的一項絕密計劃&mdash;&mdash;戰士再造計劃，通過藥物注射等手段將士兵大造成冷血無情、實力強悍的超級戰士。隨著技術不斷改進，在羅伯特&middot;柯林博士的主持下又開啟了白塔計劃，成功打造出更為完美的第二代超級戰士。然而一次意外後12名二代戰士逃亡，而涉嫌叛國的柯林博士也被驅逐東歐。此後不久，再造戰士佔領切爾諾貝利，美國軍方決定派出4名尚存的一代戰士前...<br />\n<br />\n4.約翰（史考特艾德金斯 飾）從昏迷中醒來後，發現他的妻女皆在家中被殘酷謀殺，他誓言追殺他依稀記得的兇手路克（尚克勞德范達美 飾），當他正努力拼湊記憶中的真相時，同時卻也被兇狠的再造戰士追緝。正當約翰一步步逼近路克，以安德魯（杜夫朗格 飾）為首並更強更猛的紅色大軍，也如從地獄歸來般迎接著他，約翰發現更多關於自己的事實，並開始質疑自己所相信的一切究竟是真是假？<br />\n<br />\n9 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5hnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=5e2cdd54\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5hnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=e815a7e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac43a854df2dcfb5d838c3e7f7d84084bb4204c","tid":2163100,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:54:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4082233a6cd861b2b4a120f9d27d71cf47ce346","tid":2163100,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T13:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be490e0aac212b1421ca3c63b59b863eaf4fe4f6","tid":2163100,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T13:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇住V台先,OKRU果邊收收地皮"},{"pid":"a01d2499bde53ac175a99c106b2c9d0824f5fa50","tid":2163100,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T15:35:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618390fdc1ab654d3888445beaceb9f0eb9c267d","tid":2163100,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T19:13:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}